Class EquipmentEnchantmentRefs

Constant references to BlueprintEquipmentEnchantment blueprints

Inheritance
System.Object
EquipmentEnchantmentRefs
Namespace: BlueprintCore.Blueprints.References
Assembly: BlueprintCore.dll
Syntax
public static class EquipmentEnchantmentRefs
Remarks

The All field is a list with a reference to all blueprints.

If you need a different reference type you can cast using Cast<T>()

.
